id: pm-bwlz
title: "ADR: Never-block agent UX: high-frequency aliases are executable bootstrap rewrites, not suggestion text"
description: "Never-block agent UX: high-frequency aliases are executable bootstrap rewrites, not suggestion text"
type: Decision
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: adr,agent-ux,architecture,"area:cli"
